de: Amendment No. 3 to the Project Agreement between Switzerland represented by the State Secretariat for Economic Affairs (seco) and Hungary represented by the Prime Minister's Office as the acting National Coordination Unit (NCU) concerning the Grant for the Project "Fully comprehensive waste control - including the control of transportation - within the territory of cognizance of the middle-Danube-Valley environmental, nature and water inspectorate" - 29-07-2016 - Projektabkommen zwischen der Schweiz, vertreten durch das SECO, und Ungarn, vertreten durch die nationale Entwicklungsagentur als nationale Koordinationseinheit, betreffend das Projekt "Verbesserung von Überwachung und Vollzug im Abfallbereich im mittleren Donautal"
en: Amendment No. 3 to the Project Agreement between Switzerland represented by the State Secretariat for Economic Affairs (seco) and Hungary represented by the Prime Minister's Office as the acting National Coordination Unit (NCU) concerning the Grant for the Project "Fully comprehensive waste control - including the control of transportation - within the territory of cognizance of the middle-Danube-Valley environmental, nature and water inspectorate" - 29-07-2016 - Project Agreement between Switzerland represented by the State Secretariat for Economic Affairs (seco) and Hungary represented by the National Development Agency as the National Coordination Unit (NCU) concerning the Grant for the Project "Fully comprehensive waste control - including the control of transportation - within the territory of cognizance of the middle-danube-valley environmental, nature and water inspectorate"
fr: Amendment No. 3 to the Project Agreement between Switzerland represented by the State Secretariat for Economic Affairs (seco) and Hungary represented by the Prime Minister's Office as the acting National Coordination Unit (NCU) concerning the Grant for the Project "Fully comprehensive waste control - including the control of transportation - within the territory of cognizance of the middle-Danube-Valley environmental, nature and water inspectorate" - 29-07-2016 - Accord de projet entre la Suisse, représentée par le SECO, et la Hongrie, representée par l'Agence de développement national comme unité de coordination nationale, concernant le projet de contrôle et de réduction d'émissions de substances polluantes dans la vallée du Danube
